name: qcachegrind074-x86
desc: 从VerySleep导出函数性能数据到QCacheGrind进行树状分析
keyword: This tool allows visualisation of profiling data in the callgrind-format.KCachegrind visualizes traces generated by profiling, including a tree map and a call graph visualization of the calls happening. It's designed to be fast for very large programs like KDE applications.
